{"type": "article", "id": 2652, "title": "Imperial Drip 咖啡机", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-30T07:43:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232347kXxEhzdqVatbZuB8.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国品牌  Proper Coffee 日前推出一款名为“ Imperial Drip ”的咖啡机，需要花费 4 小时才能煮出一壶咖啡，这漫长的过程只为提升咖啡的口感，减少酸度。水滴式咖啡口感之所以不涩，是因为使用冷水。其他咖啡冲煮法多使用热水冲煮，而温度太高的热水会使咖啡中某些化学物质分解出来，释出涩味，而水滴式咖啡完全以冷水滴滤，咖啡百分之百浸透湿润，萃取出的咖啡口感滑顺而不酸涩。如此说来，漫长的等待似乎也是值得的。目前，Imperial Drip 正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/billabbe/imperial-proper-coffee-drip\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上众筹。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323450MstIaJfnvYmxF1C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232345siSHIZ5qA41haB9v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232345lWtUOp8qa34rVjAx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232346oOndJMKch29sDHxq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}